0DEcontrol_1 ### 2.4 MA MA-plotlog2 fold changeM-valueA-valueMyAxcontrol_2treatment_1

M <- logdata$control_2 - logdata$treatment_1                        ## M-value
A <- (logdata$control_2 + logdata$treatment_1)/2                    ## 
judge <- sapply(M, function(x , threshold = 1){                     ## 1up, down, none
  if(x > threshold){x = 'up'
  } else if (x < -threshold){x = 'down'
  } else {x = 'none'}
})

MA = data.frame(A, M)
ggplot(MA, aes(x = A, y = M)) +                                     
  geom_point(aes(color=judge), size = 1.5, alpha = 1/5) +           ## judge
  geom_hline(aes(yintercept=0), color = "blue3") +                  ## 
  stat_smooth(se = FALSE, method = "loess", color = "red3") +       ## loess
  scale_color_manual(values=c("forestgreen", "grey", "firebrick1")) ##
